SUMMARY:Spring in Motion BINGO Begins!
DESCRIPTION:Join the Center Fitness Club’s Spring into Motion BINGO Challenge!\n\n\n\n\n\nGoal: Complete 5 in a row from March 1 – April 30.\nJoin the challenge at the CFC front desk! Cards will be posted at the front of the CFC for you to update and track your progress.\nAll cards with a BINGO will be entered into a raffle for fun prizes!\n\nMust be a member at the Center Fitness Club to participate. Learn more about the club HERE! \n\n\n\n  \n  Download PDF\n      \n          \n          \n           Save This Page as a PDF
