SUMMARY:TGIF Skate
DESCRIPTION:T.G.I.F. Skate\nat Centennial Ice Rinks (2300 Old Glenview Rd.) \n\nFriday\, March 20\n7-8:30 pm\nGeneral Admission: $10 (Skate Rental: $5)\n\nThank Goodness It’s Friday returns! This classic Public Skate event features music\, giveaways\, country-western themed attire\, games and\, of course\, ice skating. Come ready to skate and play! \n\n  \n  Download PDF\n      \n          \n          \n           Save This Page as a PDF
