SUMMARY:Bunny Brunch & Egg Hunts
DESCRIPTION:Bunny Brunch at Lakeview Center\n\nMarch 22 at 9 am and 10:45 am\nAge 2 & up with adult\nR-$24 / NR-$30\nREGISTER NOW!\n\nDon’t miss out on the chance to have brunch with the Easter Bunny at the Lakeview Center before (or after) the Easter Egg Hunt! While enjoying a delicious breakfast and refreshments with your family\, you can also take memorable photos with the Easter Bunny. Remember to register beforehand in order to secure your spot for this delightful experience.\n\n\n\nChildren’s Egg Hunt\n\nMarch 22 at 10:15 am (check-in 9:45-10:10 am)\nAge 1-10 (groups for 1-2\, 3-4\, 5-7 & 8-10)\nR-$12 / NR-$15\nREGISTER NOW!\n\nJoin us for our annual Easter Egg hunt at Gillson Park! Bring a basket or bag to collect colorful eggs filled with candy and toys! Eggs are dispersed across specified grassy sections and children will participate in their age group: 1-2\, 3-4\, 5-7\, 8-10 years old. Only parents/guardians of the 1-2 age group are permitted on the field. Visit the Bunny and take your photo before or after the event!\n\n\n\nDoggie Egg Hunt\n\n\nMarch 22 at 11:15 am (check-in 10:45-11:10 am)\nAge 18 & up (groups for  small dogs and medium/large dogs)\nR-$12 / NR-$15\nREGISTER NOW!\n\nYour dog will help sniff out eggs that are filled with treats at Gillson Park! One handler per dog who must be 18 years of age or older. All dogs must remain on-leash for the entire event and be at least 4 months old to participate and wearing current rabies tags. Both hunts will take place at the same time on different fields. After the event make sure to grab a picture with the Easter Bunny! Please bring your own bag or basket. Fee is per dog. Kindly sponsored by Kriser’s in Wilmette! \n** Please note\, this hunt is specifically for dogs. Handlers may guide dogs to eggs\, but must not hunt for eggs on their own. \n\n\n  \n  Download PDF\n      \n          \n          \n           Save This Page as a PDF
URL:https://wilmettepark.org/event-list/bunny-brunch-egg-hunts/
LOCATION:Lakeview Center\, 800 Gillson Park Dr.\, Wilmette\, IL\, 60091\, United States
CATEGORIES:Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://d11ixze0kvt635.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/06113133/BBEH26-Fi.jpg
END:VEVENT
